rows.label: bf07080100_0010
rows.name:
Homura thought you'd be better off if she was dead,
did you know that?

rows.label: bf07080100_0022
rows.name: is planning to sacrifice herself to defeat them!

rows.label: bf07080100_0040
rows.name:
You drove her to this,
but here you are, giving up.

rows.label: bf07080100_0050
rows.name:
You said you'd get Homura to Eden, didn't you?
You'll eat your words, just like that?

rows.label: bf07080100_0060
rows.name:
Hey, Mum... Dad...
It's been a while.

rows.label: bf07080100_0070
rows.name:
A ton happened, you know - I became
a Driver!

rows.label: bf07080100_0100
rows.name: She's a very important person, to me.

rows.label: bf07080100_0110
rows.name: We- we're going to Eden. Homura and me.

rows.label: bf07080100_0120
rows.name: I don't know what's coming next, but...

rows.label: bf07080100_0130
rows.name: You'll be watching over us, right guys?
